<template>
 

</template>
<script setup>
import { useStore } from "vuex";
import { computed, onMounted, ref } from "vue";
import { axiosGet } from "@/services/service";
const store = useStore();
const allJobs = computed(() => {
  return store.state.contractor.allJobs;
});
const jobCatogories = ref(null);
onMounted(async () => {
  const result = await axiosGet("/getCategories");
  jobCatogories.value = result.data;
  console.log(allJobs.value);
  console.log(jobCatogories.value);
});
</script>
<style scoped></style>
